  "body": "![Awesome Dungeon Header ](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/ptzsjBKT/images/863e9b5c0e3c89df67cf8d0c82a2049e42c7d4ef.png)\n\n## Intro :\n\nTransform your Minecraft world with a variety of exciting and diverse dungeons scattered across the overworld! Each dungeon is meticulously designed to offer an immersive exploration experience, filled with hidden loot, challenging mobs, and dynamic environments. Whether you’re navigating through lush jungles, arid deserts, or eerie swamps, these dungeons bring new challenges and rewards for players looking to expand their adventure.\n\n- 🌳 The Giant Jungle Tree\n- 🏯 Abandoned Oak Palace\n- 🏰 Better Default Temple Jungle\n- 🏰 The Swamp Temple\n- 🏜️ Desert Temple Husk\n- 🏰 The Z Thower\n- 🍄 Mushroom Abandonned\n- 🏚️ The Usine\n- 🏰 Witch Castle \n\n## Discover More Amazing Mods!\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/better-village\"\n  title=\"Download Better Villages - Improve Minecraft Villages\"\n  target=\"_blank\"\n  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n  <img alt=\"Better Villages - Enhance and Improve Minecraft Villages\"\n    src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/dGVX5JbJ/37fb0191b7d0da4db6440b5ceb705e3eea0e6e35_96.webp\" />\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/awesome-dungeon-nether\"\n  title=\"Download Awesome Dungeon: Nether Edition - Dangerous Nether Dungeons\"\n  target=\"_blank\"\n  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n  <img\n    alt=\"Awesome Dungeon Nether Edition - Survive Deadly Nether Dungeons\"\n    src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/gW1httFP/2b963bb4be8659f1f3492100aa9c48066ab699f0_96.webp\" />\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/awesome-dungeon-edition-ocean\"\n  title=\"Download Awesome Dungeon: Ocean Edition - Underwater Dungeons Adventure\"\n  target=\"_blank\"\n  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n  <img\n    alt=\"Awesome Dungeon Ocean Edition - Discover Submerged Dungeons and Treasures\"\n    src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/hn56Bq5n/0b21eff420e6c04c3820efebd77ab9bf2ee82d76_96.webp\" />\n</a>\n<a hre